### Variables
@gatewayUrl = http://localhost:8080
@inventoryUrl = http://localhost:8082
@authUrl = http://localhost:8083

### ===================================================
### AUTH SERVICE
### ===================================================

### Login como admin → copiá el token en @token
### @name loginAdmin
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Login como user
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### ===================================================
### INVENTORY SERVICE — vía API Gateway (con JWT)
### ===================================================

@token = Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}

### Obtener todos los productos
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener producto por ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear producto
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto Test",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 99.99
}

###

### ===================================================
### CLIENTE SERVICE — vía API Gateway (con JWT)
### ===================================================

### Crear cliente
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Cliente Demo",
  "telefono": "+54 11 1234-5678"
}

###

### Listar clientes
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener cliente por ID (cambiar 1 por un ID real)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Actualizar cliente por ID
PUT {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Cliente Demo Editado",
  "telefono": "+54 11 7000-0000"
}

###

### Eliminar cliente por ID
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear cliente inválido (esperado: 400)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "",
  "telefono": "x"
}

###

### Obtener cliente inexistente (esperado: 404)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes/999999999
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Sin JWT en endpoint protegido (esperado: 401)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/clientes

###

### ===================================================
### INVENTORY SERVICE — acceso directo (sin gateway)
### ===================================================

### Obtener todos los productos (directo)
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Obtener producto por ID (directo)
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products/1
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Crear producto (directo)
POST {{inventoryUrl}}/api/inventory/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto Directo",
  "quantity": 5,
  "price": 49.99
}

###

### ===================================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### ===================================================

### Eureka
GET http://localhost:8761/actuator/health

###

### Config Server
GET http://localhost:8888/actuator/health

###

### Inventory Service
GET {{inventoryUrl}}/actuator/health

###

### Cliente Service
GET http://localhost:8086/actuator/health

###

### API Gateway
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/actuator/health

###

### Auth Service
GET {{authUrl}}/actuator/health

###

